### Sample JSON body (create / update) — same shape for POST and PUT
#
# {
#   "tradeId": "T-2026-0001",
#   "symbol": "AAPL",
#   "side": "BUY",
#   "quantity": 100.5000,
#   "price": 182.3500,
#   "status": "NEW",
#   "eventTimestamp": "2026-04-03T14:30:00",
#   "sourceSystem": "OMS-1"
# }
#
# Allowed side: BUY, SELL (case-insensitive; stored uppercase)
# Allowed status: NEW, AMENDED, CANCELLED, COMPLETED (case-insensitive; stored uppercase)

### POST create trade
POST http://localhost:8080/project/api/trades
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tradeId": "T-2026-0001",
  "symbol": "AAPL",
  "side": "BUY",
  "quantity": 100.5000,
  "price": 182.3500,
  "status": "NEW",
  "eventTimestamp": "2026-04-03T14:30:00",
  "sourceSystem": "OMS-1"
}

### GET all trades
GET http://localhost:8080/project/api/trades

### GET trade by database id (replace 1)
GET http://localhost:8080/project/api/trades/1

### GET trade by business tradeId
GET http://localhost:8080/project/api/trades/business/T-2026-0001

### PUT update trade (replace 1)
PUT http://localhost:8080/project/api/trades/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tradeId": "T-2026-0001",
  "symbol": "AAPL",
  "side": "SELL",
  "quantity": 50.0000,
  "price": 190.0000,
  "status": "AMENDED",
  "eventTimestamp": "2026-04-03T15:00:00",
  "sourceSystem": "OMS-1"
}

### DELETE trade (replace 1)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/project/api/trades/1
